I was not going to put, I was not going to talk about this, Brian, because I don't want to, you know, this is not like TMZ bites.

00:29:49.520 --> 00:29:50.340
Bite on bites.

00:29:50.820 --> 00:29:55.700
There's a lot of drama here, but I think it's pervasive enough that I think we should put it on people's radar.

00:29:55.700 --> 00:30:03.860
So, I'm not here, what I'm about to describe, I'm not here to take sides in, I'm not here to, like, put bad light on anybody,

00:30:04.040 --> 00:30:11.300
but there's a mad level of turmoil around the encode projects.

00:30:12.920 --> 00:30:24.580
