Michael says, I forked HTTPX to HTTPXXY.

00:31:03.400 --> 00:31:04.420
Talks about why.

00:31:05.480 --> 00:31:10.880
Transfer of UVicorn and Starlette causes a great bunch of stirs.

00:31:11.500 --> 00:31:14.460
